ull, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/791c/37c0/562494_mini.png?m=1639064946", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/791c/37c0/562494_normal.png?m=1639064946", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/791c/37c0/562494_large.png?m=1639064946", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/791c/37c0/562494_xlarge.png?m=1639064946", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/791c/37c0/562494_xlarge.png?m=1639064946", "created": 1637489859, "last_modified": 1639064946}, "last_reply_by": "fivesmallq", "last_touched": 1654489147, "title": "都说 4K 屏细腻，可是我今天连接上后感觉颗粒感很重呀", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/857432", "created": 1654440112, "deleted": 0, "content": "型号 Up600 ，连 MBP14 请问如何设置", "content_rendered": "型号 Up600 ，连 MBP14 请问如何设置", "last_modified": 1654440112, "replies": 41, "id": 857432}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 18533, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2172, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 427777, "username": "KanadeCCCC", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/KanadeCCCC", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6f7c/39e1/427777_mini.png?m=1565250369", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6f7c/39e1/427777_normal.png?m=1565250369", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6f7c/39e1/427777_large.png?m=1565250369", "created": 1562567220, "last_modified": 1565250369}, "last_reply_by": "moooookey", "last_touched": 1654484559, "title": "说说看大家心目中的 iPad /iPadOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/857375", "created": 1654409868, "deleted": 0, "content": "## 题主先来,基础信息\r\n1. iPad Pro 12.9 2021 款\r\n2. 秒控键盘\r\n3. Apple Pencil 二代\r\n4. iPadOS 15.5\r\n\r\n\r\n### 对在用 iPad/iPadOS 满意的地方\r\n1. 系统长期稳定\r\n2. 屏幕优秀\r\n3. 音响效果好\r\n4. 手写笔与键盘操作优秀\r\n\r\n### 对在用 iPad/iPadOS 不满意的地方\r\n1. M1+Mini LED 的屏幕，电池续航很不理想\r\n2. 隔空投送的少见文件格式，需要有能打开的指定软件保存\r\n3. 分屏与小窗的操作逻辑稍微复杂了点\r\n4. 太重\r\n5. 回收铝外壳不是很可靠（题主出现过 iPhone 掉到 iPad 边缘砸了一个小坑出来的情况）\r\n\r\n### 希望 iPad/iPadOS 能改变 /优化的地方\r\n1. 开放高权限的终端，开放 iPad 本地开发\r\n2. 提升硬件可靠度（不戴壳使用起来很爽）\r\n3. 减轻重量（妙控键盘太重）\r\n4. 增加 iPad 摄像头使用场景\r\n5. 新增官方计算器", "content_rendered": "<h2>题主先来,基础信息</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>iPad Pro 12.9 2021 款</li>\n<li>秒控键盘</li>\n<li>Apple Pencil 二代</li>\n<li>iPadOS 15.5</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>对在用 iPad/iPadOS 满意的地方</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>系统长期稳定</li>\n<li>屏幕优秀</li>\n<li>音响效果好</li>\n<li>手写笔与键盘操作优秀</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>对在用 iPad/iPadOS 不满意的地方</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>M1+Mini LED 的屏幕，电池续航很不理想</li>\n<li>隔空投送的少见文件格式，需要有能打开的指定软件保存</li>\n<li>分屏与小窗的操作逻辑稍微复杂了点</li>\n<li>太重</li>\n<li>回收铝外壳不是很可靠（题主出现过 iPhone 掉到 iPad 边缘砸了一个小坑出来的情况）</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>希望 iPad/iPadOS 能改变 /优化的地方</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>开放高权限的终端，开放 iPad 本地开发</li>\n<li>提升硬件可靠度（不戴壳使用起来很爽）</li>\n<li>减轻重量（妙控键盘太重）</li>\n<li>增加 iPad 摄像头使用场景</li>\n<li>新增官方计算器</li>\n</ol>\n", "last_modified": 1654409893, "replies": 36, "id": 857375}]